Installation/Configuration of TestNG:
1. Google ===> testng download testng.org ===> u will get url - http://beust.com/eclipse.
2. Open Eclipse ===> Help ===> Install New Software ===> Paste the copied URL under "work with" field.
3. TestNG will be displayed with a check box ===>  Check it ===> Next ===> Finish

Verify if TestNG is installed:
1. Eclipse ===> Windows ===> show view ===> other ===> java ===>TestNg(if TestNG is available means success)
